text: Jackson Kasanga Mulwa (1942 - 16 March 2015) was a Kenyan judge and politician. Mulwa was a judge on the East African Court of Justice, as well as a Member of Parliament representing Makueni Constituency from 1969 to 1983. ==References== Category:2015 deaths Category:East African Court of Justice judges Category:Kenyan judges Category:Members of the National Assembly (Kenya) Category:1942 births Category:Kenyan judges of international courts and tribunals
